  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"font-size:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:12px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:8px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(238, 238, 238) 0px, rgb(238, 238, 238) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 32px), repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgb(238, 238, 238) 0px, rgb(238, 238, 238) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 32px) rgb(245, 245, 245);font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT 更新，企业版新增：</span>\n    <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);\">\n    <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">公司知识（Company Knowledge）</span></strong></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 16px;margin:0px 8px 32px;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 4px 6px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单来说</span></strong>\n     <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT 现在能连你公司的各种内部工具，从 Slack、Google Drive、GitHub、SharePoint 这些地方找信息，然后给你一个综合答案，带引用</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键信息</span></strong></p>\n   <ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 0.2em;margin:0px 12px 0em 16px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;list-style:disc;text-align:left;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 只给 Business、Enterprise、Edu 版开放</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 用了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">特调的 GPT-5</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，专精于多源检索</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 答案会标注来源，可以点开看原文</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 有公司级别的权限，你看不到的别人也看不到</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"307\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYoz7MHCwNiaXBkM4T46Osh4HhfozDWV1p3ztiaicYWyRVCzLll8bugXKibJ0ZQcr8bOMo89ic2pR7YbiaicQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"307\" data-imgfileid=\"100023881\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;border-style:solid;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;text-align:left;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;margin:0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6dbae1a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYoz7MHCwNiaXBkM4T46Osh4HhfozDWV1p3ztiaicYWyRVCzLll8bugXKibJ0ZQcr8bOMo89ic2pR7YbiaicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">回答的时候，会查找大量公司内部文件</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 19.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(198, 110, 73);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么用</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在订阅了 ChatGPT 的企业版之后，点击输入框下面的「Company knowledge」按钮，启用该功能</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYoz7MHCwNiaXBkM4T46Osh4Hj5ddCSCia8c1iapZviad3BXX96SNRJ4xslTfm5Wn1YFeweXcNvaonN37g/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"307\" data-imgfileid=\"100023880\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);display: block;vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;height: auto;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6cc946ab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYoz7MHCwNiaXBkM4T46Osh4Hj5ddCSCia8c1iapZviad3BXX96SNRJ4xslTfm5Wn1YFeweXcNvaonN37g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">下方有个按钮「Company knowledge」...</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">搜索过程会在侧边栏显示，你能看到它在查什么、找到了什么</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">答案出来后，会列出所有用到的来源，点进去就能看原文</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: bord