igure>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">扫 GitHub 仓库的待办事项、Linear 的工单、Slack 工程频道的讨论，列出哪些完成了、哪些卡住了、哪些还没记录</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 19.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(198, 110, 73);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据安全</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 强调了几点：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 0.2em;margin:0px 12px 0em 16px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;list-style:disc;text-align:left;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 企业管理员可以控制哪些应用能连、谁能用</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• ChatGPT 只能访问用户本身有权限看的内容</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 不会用你的数据训练模型</span></strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 所有数据传输都加密</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 支持 SSO、SCIM、IP 白名单</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 管理员可以通过 Compliance API 查看对话记录</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;margin:0px;let